## Palmer Penguins

This is a test of Quarto functionality using the Palmer Penguins package.

```{r}
 library(tidyverse)
    library(palmerpenguins)
    
    penguins %>% head()

```

This code loads the `palmerpenguins` package and displays the top (or `head`) of the dataset.
